{"tid":1222682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賢者會師】多個國際律師組織 促請擱置修訂逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T22:17:57.000Z","uid":138409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"558f5ff292bf726c4a48370321c38df9b216c865","tid":1222682,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭：<br />\n英格蘭大律師人權委員會、英格蘭律師公會、國際大律師公會、國際引渡法專家、國際公平審訊權NGO，全部都唔理解法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府將會繼續解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n20號就通過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又，依家真係好似RPG打魔王咁<br />\n唔單止僧侶<br />\n連賢者都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.barhumanrights.org.uk/hong-kongs-ill-conceived-extradition-proposals-fundamentally-imperil-the-operation-of-the-rule-of-law-say-leading-international-law-organisations/?fbclid=IwAR0RXnIv8vtBTtQ5sJBLUOjxRBView3W73TEy1FYf-YjRpYjnACWPtHggx0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.barhumanrights.org.uk%2Fhong-kongs-ill-conceived-extradition-proposals-fundamentally-imperil-the-operation-of-the-rule-of-law-say-leading-international-law-organisations%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0RXnIv8vtBTtQ5sJBLUOjxRBView3W73TEy1FYf-YjRpYjnACWPtHggx0&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjeSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=34225c83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.barhumanrights.org.uk/hong-kongs-ill-conceived-extradition-proposals-fundamentally-imperil-the-operation-of-the-rule-of-law-say-leading-international-law-organisations/?fbclid=IwAR0RXnIv8vtBTtQ5sJBLUOjxRBView3W73TEy1FYf-YjRpYjnACWPtHggx0</a><br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n（基本上大家都聽過好多次，今次純粹係國際組織都要出聲明咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n-- 無法保障人權以及法治，因為目前修訂草案中有關人權審視的權力，完全集中在特首身上；考慮到其職責以及委任性質，無法不偏不倚獨立地做決定<br />\n--目前條例修訂下，法院無權因申請引渡的國家的人權狀況 而拒絕申請"},{"pid":"2789aaf8a488d13d8c47086115c4ffc44e986804","tid